Interface IInitialSdDelayConfig

  • All Superinterfaces:
    IEntity

    public interface IInitialSdDelayConfig
extends IEntity
    IInitialSdDelayConfig: Entity class of the tresosDB model.

    This element is used to configure the offer behavior of the server and the find behavior on the client.
